{"tid":1246551,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日衝擺明係個陷阱啦","createTime":"2019-06-20T18:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T00:44:37.000Z","uid":154223,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"09202d4e6f60d32b0669d4cf803845ee9624687d","tid":1246551,"uid":154223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:20:43.000Z","msg":"呢度一叫人唔好勇武就話人係鬼，我話如果係咪都叫人聽日衝果D先係。<br />\n 聽日立法會取消左國歌法二讀政府又暫停辦公，班高官又扮哂道歉又話會同年輕人溝通，我地今次禁難得攞埋中年果堆人嘅支持，如果聽日衝就擺明係個陷阱。你地唔記得之前有隻狗扮示威者最尾俾人推跌即刻show 委任證咩？<br />\n<br />\n我係政棍就喺連登開個post 屌大家唔敢衝，然後放D鬼引人衝，或者帶頭倒亂，務求和理非同我地撕裂，分化我地。烈士頭七都未過，唔好忘記佢嘅遺言 - 我們不是暴動，如果聽日衰呢樣咁所有野都前功盡廢嫁啦⋯<br />\n<br />\n總之一句，大家聽日小心，唔好中陷阱！"},{"pid":"0e862ee61448fd101d777ee9f56b2fb19782ab3a","tid":1246551,"uid":1354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"第一個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aecaa08f32686a0aab06a40517f7cc2716982a59","tid":1246551,"uid":124372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:23:01.000Z","msg":"明天應該都係乜事都無最開心係班公務員<br />\n又有假放"},{"pid":"846dc62a028f05f330ec8cc09c44b47784d80d35","tid":1246551,"uid":50363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5553566bddc14ea1a23e4e99af455567e47a10","tid":1246551,"uid":50363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371c005257b0d291bd344d4898e5a8052665c644","tid":1246551,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:29:17.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399528334593c241224d1f5b76b21c2d34676fba","tid":1246551,"uid":154223,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"0e862ee61448fd101d777ee9f56b2fb19782ab3a","tid":1246551,"uid":1354,"like":2,"d